These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, dancing, rock-climbing, magic-tricks, collecting
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, indie, jazz, pop, soul
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
5. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is in the middle##1
7. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Hobby   | dancing | rock-climbing | cooking | collecting | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | dubstep | jazz     | pop       | indie  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, soy-milk, sprite
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: aconite, iris, tulip, begonia, marigold
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
5. the person drinking coffee is the person who growstulip##1
6. the person who growsmarigold is the person drinking sprite##1
7. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Beverage      | coffee | fanta | almond-milk | soy-milk | sprite |
| Flower   | tulip  | begonia   | aconite       | iris    | marigold   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
City: venice, london, berlin, nizza, liverpool
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, bus, jet-ski, ship, subway
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the person traveling to london is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| City        | berlin | nizza | london | venice | liverpool |
| Transport   | bus  | boat      | subway | jet-ski | ship      |

