.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, fishing, reading, sudoku, traveling
There 5 different types of food: blueberry, peas, apricot, peach, cranberry
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person eating peas##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person eating peas##1
3. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the person eating apricot is on the far right##1
7. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Hobby   | sudoku    | baking        | reading | fishing | traveling |
| Food     | blueberry | peach | cranberry  | peas   | apricot |

