.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
There 5 different types of food: banana, cherry, grapes, mango, strawberry
The people have 5 different jobs:  bartender, security-guard, engineer, scientist, coach
1. the scientist is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the security-guard is the person eating strawberry##1
3. the engineer is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the engineer is in the middle##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating banana##1
6. the coach is the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Food    | grapes   | banana     | cherry   | mango         | strawberry |
| Job   | bartender | scientist | engineer | coach | security-guard     |

