.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
5 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, pony, rabbit, rat
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, roller, airplane, bus
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the bike is the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the roller is the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Pet     | frog   | pony  | rat      | chinchilla | rabbit     |
| Transport   | airplane | roller | jet-ski | bike   | bus |

