.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
5 different pets are kept: pony, lizard, horse, goat, guinea-pig
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, soccer, tennis, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Pet     | lizard | pony       | guinea-pig | goat | horse    |
| Sport   | tennis   | water-polo | soccer  | rugby     | ice-hockey |

