.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: parkour, swimming, lacrosse, tennis, volleyball
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, classical, house, indie, rock
1. the fan of house is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
5. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of classical##1
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is the fan of classical##1
7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Sport         | tennis | parkour | lacrosse | volleyball | swimming |
| Music-Genre   | house       | indie   | rock         | classical   | blues   |

