2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the owner of the frog is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is in the middle##1
6. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
| Beverage   | coffee | 7up | almond-milk | water | hot-chocolate |
| Pet           | rat      | fish    | goldfish  | dog     | frog     |

