.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-14::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, sprite
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, april, february, december, september
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | sprite | hot-chocolate | cola      | soy-milk | fanta      |
| Birthday   | april  | december       | october | september  | february |

