.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-15::.
House: tower, palace, gothic-revival, cape-cod, art-deco
There are 5 different nationalities: colombian, french, indian, nigerian, thai
1. the nigerian is on the right of the indian##1
2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the thai##1
3. the art-deco house is on the left of the tower house##1
4. the indian is the gothic-revival house##1
5. the palace house is on the far right##1
6. the french is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
7. the thai is on the left of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |     3      |   4    |    5     |
| House           | cape-cod     | art-deco | tower | gothic-revival  | palace |
| Nationality   | colombian | thai               | french     | indian | nigerian |

