4. the person eating apricot is on the left of the colonial house##1
5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
6. the modern house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |      5      |
| Food    | asparagus   | blueberry | peach      | apricot | lime        |
| House   | art-deco | ranch-style     | modern | victorian | colonial |

