.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-18::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: magic-tricks, hiking, photography, filmmaking, fishing
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, cricket, rugby, swimming
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4      |    5     |
| Hobby   | hiking   | filmmaking  | magic-tricks | fishing | photography  |
| Sport         | badminton | cricket | rugby  | swimming    | baseball |

