.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, milk, mirinda, tea
5 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, monopoly, billiard, domino
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
4. the person playing monopoly is the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person playing domino##1
6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
7. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage   | tea     | milk       | 7up     | fanta  | mirinda  |
| Game      | billiard | snooker | mah-jongg | domino | monopoly |

