.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, romance, satire, thriller
5 different games are played: billiard, mah-jongg, bridge, monopoly, go
1. the person playing mah-jongg is in the middle##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person playing go##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | thriller | romance | documentary | satire |
| Game           | go | monopoly  | mah-jongg    | billiard  | bridge   |

 